\i\fs71\fsmilli35712 \cf2 \cb3 How it relates to investing
\i0 \cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs55\fsmilli27648 \cf2 \cb3 Many new investors haven\'92t developed a solid grasp of the investing process and tend to assume that stockbrokers and those business \'93experts\'94 who frequently appear in the media understand the topic better than they do. This can lead them to accept investment recommendations that are not based on solid research\'97or be swayed to enter the market at the peak of a cycle (a mistake often compounded when they decide to sell at the bottom of the cycle).\cb1 \
\
